cs.GT, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.DS, cs.SY 

This paper deals with decision making in a repeated game with incomplete information, which is a topic that falls under game theory (cs.GT) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also discusses policies and optimization, which are topics in machine learning (cs.LG) and data structures (cs.DS). Additionally, the paper deals with control and optimization in a dynamic system, which is a topic in systems and control (cs.SY).
